Solana Counter Program - Project Structure
==========================================

Root Level
----------
.
├── .editorconfig                # Editor configuration
├── .gitignore                   # Git ignore patterns
├── .prettierrc                  # Prettier configuration
├── .prettierignore              # Prettier ignore patterns
├── Anchor.toml                  # Anchor workspace configuration (devnet)
├── Cargo.toml                   # Rust workspace configuration
├── Makefile                     # Build automation commands
├── package.json                 # Node.js dependencies (Anchor tests)
├── tsconfig.json                # TypeScript configuration (tests)
├── yarn.lock                    # Yarn lock file
├── LICENSE                      # MIT License
├── README.md                    # Main documentation
├── QUICKSTART.md                # Quick start guide
└── CONTRIBUTING.md              # Contribution guidelines

Smart Contract
--------------
programs/
└── counter-program/
    ├── Cargo.toml              # Program dependencies
    └── src/
        └── lib.rs              # Counter program implementation
                                 # - initialize instruction
                                 # - increment instruction
                                 # - Counter account structure
                                 # - Error handling

Tests
-----
tests/
└── counter-program.ts           # Comprehensive test suite
                                 # - Initialize test
                                 # - Increment test
                                 # - Multiple increments test
                                 # - Authority validation test

Frontend
--------
frontend/
├── package.json                 # Frontend dependencies
├── tsconfig.json               # TypeScript config
├── next.config.js              # Next.js configuration
├── tailwind.config.js          # Tailwind CSS config
├── postcss.config.js           # PostCSS config
├── .eslintrc.json             # ESLint config
├── .env.example               # Environment variables template
└── src/                       # Source code
    ├── app/                   # Next.js app directory
    ├── components/            # React components
    ├── hooks/                # Custom hooks
    └── lib/                  # Utility libraries

Backend
-------
backend/
└── README.md                   # Backend placeholder documentation

Scripts
-------
scripts/
├── README.md                   # Scripts documentation
├── deploy.sh                   # Interactive deployment script
└── setup-local.sh              # Local development setup

Migrations
----------
migrations/
└── deploy.ts                   # Anchor deployment migration

Key Features
------------
✅ Anchor-based Solana smart contract
✅ Initialize and increment counter operations
✅ Authority validation and overflow protection
✅ Comprehensive test suite
✅ Devnet-ready configuration
✅ Deployment automation scripts
✅ Next.js frontend with wallet integration
✅ Full documentation and guides

Build Artifacts (git-ignored)
------------------------------
target/                         # Rust build output
node_modules/                   # Node.js dependencies
.anchor/                        # Anchor cache
test-ledger/                    # Local validator data
.next/                          # Next.js build output

